---
title: Pak Choi Turkey Mince Noodles with ketjap manis and coriander
description: A more nutritious take on a classic option, pork or beef mince is replaced by turkey in this delicious dish. Soy sauce brings the element of umami while a vibrant scattered scallion garnish adds brightness and crunch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R18_W08_IE_IEXCT18821-2__MAIN_high-88249510.jpg
